:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CENX\" title=\"Century Aluminum Company\">CENX</a></span>) is a high-momentum stock that stands to benefit significantly if the incoming Trump administration imposes 25% tariffs on imports from Canada, which accounts for about 60% of the total tonnage of aluminum that</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/927991642/image_927991642.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742380-century-aluminum-well-positioned-to-gain-from-trump-tariffs", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 20:19:10"}, {"id": "4742395", "title": "Brown-Forman Corporation 2025 Q2 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Brown-Forman Corporation in conjunction with their 2025 Q2 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106049\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742395-brown-forman-corporation-2025-q2-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 20:13:22"}, {"id": "4742378", "title": "Sky Harbour Group: A Unique Business Model", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442422207/image_1442422207.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Large aircraft in aircraft maintenance hangar\" data-id=\"1442422207\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442422207/image_1442422207.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442422207/image_1442422207.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442422207/image_1442422207.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442422207/image_1442422207.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.