</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412721464/image_1412721464.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742176-nvidia-this-is-only-the-beginning", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 20:00:00"}, {"id": "4742371", "title": "TD Bank: A U.S. Exit Looks Probable", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458302051/image_458302051.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"TD Bank Sign in New York CY\" data-id=\"458302051\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458302051/image_458302051.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458302051/image_458302051.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458302051/image_458302051.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458302051/image_458302051.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458302051/image_458302051.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458302051/image_458302051.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458302051/image_458302051.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458302051/image_458302051.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">omada/iStock Unreleased via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em><strong>All values are in CAD unless noted otherwise.</strong></em></p> <p>Back in August, we covered the second quarter financial results of The Toronto-Dominion Bank (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TD\" title=\"The Toronto-Dominion Bank\">TD</a></span>) and the sale of a portion of its Charles Schwab Corporation (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458302051/image_458302051.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742371-td-bank-a-us-exit-looks-probable", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 19:51:20"}, {"id": "4742370", "title": "Humana: Medicare Advantage Is Just A Short-Term Problem", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2097577410/image_2097577410.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Female nurse accepting payment from patient at reception desk in doctor\"s office' data-id=\"2097577410\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2097577410/image_2097577410.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2097577410/image_2097577410.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2097577410/image_2097577410.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2097577410/image_2097577410.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2097577410/image_2097577410.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2097577410/image_2097577410.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2097577410/image_2097577410.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2097577410/image_2097577410.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">MoMo Productions/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I am updating my ongoing analysis on Humana Inc. (N<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HUM\" title=\"Humana Inc.\">HUM</a></span>).</p> <p>Previously, I rated Humana a buy for the following reasons:</p> <ul> <li>DCF analysis on reaffirmed guidance suggested a price target of $397, 10% upside from pricing at the</li> </ul>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2097577410/image_2097577410.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742370-humana-medicare-advantage-is-just-a-short-term-problem", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 19:40:23"}, {"id": "4742366", "title": "American Homes 4 Rent: Favorable Dynamics At A Fair Valuation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1556901356/image_1556901356.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Single family model homes\" data-id=\"1556901356\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"891px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1556901356/image_1556901356.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1556901356/image_1556901356.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1556901356/image_1556901356.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1556901356/image_1556901356.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1556901356/image_1556901356.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1556901356/image_1556901356.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1556901356/image_1556901356.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1556901356/image_1556901356.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Kirpal Kooner</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Shares of American Homes 4 Rent (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMH\" title=\"American Homes 4 Rent\">AMH</a></span>) have been an underperformer over the past year, rising just 5% and mostly missing out on the strong equity rally, given sluggish home prices and higher-for-longer interest rates. I last covered shares of AMH</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1556901356/image_1556901356.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742366-american-homes-4-rent-favorable-dynamics-at-a-fair-valuation", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 19:32:00"}, {"id": "4742365", "title": "Accuray Incorporated: Cheap, But With Caveats", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445308167/image_1445308167.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Cancer treatment in a modern medical private clinic or hospital with a linear accelerator. Professional doctors team working while the woman is undergoing radiation therapy for cancer\" data-id=\"1445308167\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Xesai</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Today, we are putting medical device concern <strong>Accuray Incorporated (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ARAY\" title=\"Accuray Incorporated\">ARAY</a></span>)</strong> in the spotlight. The company has a straightforward business of manufacturing and marketing radiosurgery and radiation therapy systems for the treatment of tumors. Accuray is seeing rather pedestrian sales growth in the</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742365-accuray-incorporated-cheap-but-with-caveats", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 19:31:14"}]}